{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 67,
  "title": "第六十七章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天下皆謂我道大，似不肖。夫唯大，故似不肖。若肖，久矣其細也夫！"
    },
    {
      "text": "我有三寶，持而保之。一曰慈，二曰儉，三曰不敢為天下先。慈故能勇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "儉故能廣，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不敢為天下先，故能成器長。"
    },
    {
      "text": "今舍慈且勇，"
    },
    {
      "text": "舍儉且廣，舍後且先，死矣！夫慈以戰則勝，"
    },
    {
      "text": "以守則固。天將救之，以慈衛之。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 31
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "久矣其細，猶曰其細久矣。肖，則失其所以為大矣。故曰，若肖久矣，其細也夫。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫慈，以陳則勝，以守則固，故能勇也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "節儉愛費，天下不匱，故能廣也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯後外其身，為物所歸，然後乃能立成器為天下利，為物之長也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "且，猶取也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "相慜而不避於難，故勝也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
